In the first half of the NBA game between Hawks and 76ers, scheduled for February 19 at 7:00 PM ET:

This market will resolve to "Over" if the Hawks and 76ers combine to score 124 or more points in the first half.

If the combined first half total is less than 124, this market will resolve to "Under".

The result will be determined based on the score at halftime only.

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed. If the game is canceled entirely, with no make-up game, this market will resolve 50-50.
